  <name>Clarity</name>
  <summary>Convert documents to Markdown format</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Clarity is a simple and elegant desktop application for converting various document formats to Markdown.
    </p>
    <p>
      It supports converting:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Microsoft Word documents (.docx)</li>
      <li>PDF files (.pdf)</li>
      <li>PowerPoint presentations (.pptx)</li>
      <li>Excel spreadsheets (.xlsx)</li>
      <li>HTML files (.html)</li>
      <li>And more!</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Simply open a document, click convert, and save your Markdown file. Clarity uses Microsoft's markitdown library for accurate and reliable conversions.
    </p>
  </description>

